      <div id="insideWrapper" class="cover">
      	<h5>What's Inside</h5>
             <ul class="whatsinside"> <li><img class="floatleft" src="images/2011/fpo_wi1.gif" border="0"/>Nearly <a href="browse">6000 entries</a> from esteemed Oxford works, including the recently published <em>Oxford Encyclopedia of the Islamic World</em>, and <a href="Public/whats_inside.html">more</a>.</li> <li><img class="floatleft" src="images/2011/fpo_wi2.gif" border="0"/><a href="browse?type=primary">Primary Source documents</a> with editorial commentary provide historical context for important events and major figures in the history of Islam.</li>              <li><img class="floatleft" src="images/2011/fpo_wi3.gif" border="0"/><a href="learning_resources.html">Learning Resources</a> include thematic guides, lesson plans, bibliographies, a glossary, and other useful tools.</li>              <li><img class="floatleft" src="images/2011/fpo_wi4.gif" border="0"/><a href="browse?type=illustration&amp;type=map">Images and Maps</a> provide visual perspectives on global Islam and its historical development.</li> 	     </ul>
